<h1 class="hero-h">Microsoft Copilot for Therapists And Counselors: <em>what actually works in 2026.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">Microsoft 365 Copilot is Microsoft's AI integrated natively across Outlook, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Teams. For therapists and counselors, it's most valuable for intake summaries, treatment plan drafting, clinical documentation, referral letters. This is the practical playbook.</p>
<div class="verdict"><div class="verdict-l">Short version</div><p class="verdict-p">Therapists And Counselors should use Microsoft Copilot for intake summaries, treatment plan drafting, clinical documentation, referral letters. Cost: $30/seat (M365 add-on). Microsoft Copilot is the right choice when you're heavy in Microsoft 365 and want AI embedded in the apps you already use. Most therapists and counselors see 2-4× productivity lift on the right tasks.</p></div>
</div></div>

